# django mysqldbwrapper
django mysqldbwrapper can be used for retry :<br/> 
1. MySQL server has gone away <br/>
2. Lost connection to MySQL server during query <br/>
2. Too many connections <br/>

### Installation
```
pip install django-mysqldbwrapper
```

### Get started
How to using django-mysqldbwrapper in django:

```Python
DATABASES = {
    'default': {
        'ENGINE':'mysqldbwrapper',
        ....
    },
}
```

